nt, England":"Kingston, Kent, Inglaterra, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Quando Walter de Denne II nasceu aproximadamente 1245, em Kingston, Kent, Inglaterra, seu pai, Walter de Denne, tinha 30 anos e sua mãe, Lady Sybella Dennehill, tinha 25 anos. Ele casou-se com Isabell em 1270, em Kingston, Kent, Inglaterra. Eles tiveram pelo menos 3 filhos. Sua profissão aparece como high steward of the priory of canterbury  em Kent, Inglaterra, United Kingdom. Ele faleceu em 1308, em sua cidade natal, com 64 anos."},"ro":{"about 1245–1308":"aproximativ 1245–1308","1245–1308":"1245–1308","1247–1279":"1247–1279","1275–1328":"1275–1328","1278–1346":"1278–1346","1308–Male":"1308–Decedat","1217–1256":"1217–1256","1221–1245":"1221–1245","1275":"1275","1270":"1270","1290":"1290","1217":"1217","1259":"1259","1346":"1346","1247":"1247","1279":"1279","1245":"1245","1256":"1256","1278":"1278","1221":"1221","about 1245":"aproximativ 1245","1308":"1308","1328":"1328","Dennehill, Kingston, Kent, England":"Kingston, Kent, Anglia, United Kingdom","Denne Hill, Kingston, Kent, England":"Kingston, Kent, Anglia, United Kingdom","Denne, Kingstone, Kent, England":"Kingston, Kent, Anglia, United Kingdom","Kingston, Kent, England":"Kingston, Kent, England","Kingstone, Kent, England":"Kingston, Kent, Anglia, United Kingdom"},"ru":{"about 1245–1308":"около 1245 г.–1308 г.","1245–1308":"1245г.–1308г.","1247–1279":"1247г.–1279г.","1275–1328":"1275г.–1328г.","1278–1346":"1278г.–1346г.","1308–Male":"1308г.–Умерший","1217–1256":"1217г.–1256г.","1221–1245":"1221г.–1245г.","1275":"1275 г.","1270":"1270 г.","1290":"1290 г.","1217":"1217 г.","1259":"1259 г.","1346":"1346 г.","1247":"1247 г.","1279":"1279 г.","1245":"1245 г.","1256":"1256 г.","1278":"1278 г.","1221":"1221 г.","about 1245":"около 1245 г.","1308":"1308 г.","1328":"1328 г.","Dennehill, Kingston, Kent, England":"кингстон, кэнт, Англия, Великобритания","Denne Hill, Kingston, Kent, England":"кингстон, кэнт, Англия, Великобритания","Denne, Kingstone, Kent, England":"кингстон, кэнт, Англия, Великобритания","Kingston, Kent, England":"кингстон, кэнт, Англия","Kingstone, Kent, England":"кингстон, кэнт, Англия, Великобритания","lifeSummary":"Когда Walter de Denne II родился около 1245 г. в местности кингстон, кэнт, Англия, его отцу по имени Walter de Denne было 30 лет, а матери, которую звали Lady Sybella Dennehill, 25. Он женился на женщине по имени Isabell в 1270 г. в местности кингстон, кэнт, Англия. У них было по крайней мере 3 сына.  Он работал по профессии high steward of the priory of canterbury  в местности кэнт, Англия, Великобритания. Он умер в 1308 г. в его родном городе в возрасте 64 лет."},"sm":{"about 1245–1308":"e tusa o le 1245–1308","1245–1308":"1245–1308","1247–1279":"1247–1279","1275–1328":"1275–1328","1278–1346":"1278–1346","1308–Male":"1308–Ua Maliu","1217–1256":"1217–1256","1221–1245":"1221–1245","1275":"1275","1270":"1270","1290":"1290","1217":"1217","1259":"1259","1346":"1346","1247":"1247","1279":"1279","1245":"1245","1256":"1256","1278":"1278","1221":"1221","about 1245":"e tusa o le 1245","1308":"1308","1328":"1328","Dennehill, Kingston, Kent, England":"Kingston, Kent, Egelani, United Kingdom","Denne Hill, Kingston, Kent, England":"Kingston, Kent, Egelani, United Kingdom","Denne, Kingstone, Kent, England":"Kingston, Kent, Egelani, United Kingdom","Kingston, Kent, England":"Kingston, Kent, Egelani","Kingstone, Kent, England":"Kingston, Kent, Egelani, United Kingdom"},"sk":{"about 1245–1308":"okolo 1245–1308","1245–1308":"1245–1308","1247–1279":"1247–1279","1275–1328":"1275–1328","1278–1346":"1278–1346","1308–Male":"1308–Zosnulý","1217–1256":"1217–1256","1221–1245":"1221–1245","1275":"1275","1270":"1270","1290":"1290","1217":"1217","1259":"1259","1346":"1346","1247":"1247","1279":"1279","1245":"1245","1256":"1256","1278":"1278","1221":"1221","about 1245":"okolo 1245","1308":"1308","1328":"1328","Dennehill, Kingston, Kent, England":"Kingston, Kent, Anglicko, Spojené kráľovstvo","Denne Hill, King